{"title":"人和墙","authors":["龚湘海"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":2,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人和墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龚湘海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙和人一样站立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人能行走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙却不能行走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙把世界划成许多空格子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存放梦和肉体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人常常需要墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风风雨雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙就是一种庇护"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又让世界徒生了许多峭壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阻拦着眸光与奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阻拦着相互呼唤的语言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人有时会在冲动里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在墙上碰得脸青鼻肿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被墙逼得苦闷的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人就构思天空的鸟儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多么讨厌墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但假如真的在一夜间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把所有的墙拆去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人又担心自己疯狂的脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会跌进某一种深渊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人时时都需要墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却又时时想挣脱墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此就在墙上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开了窗子和门"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}